body_html:
Marking as contributions welcome for now, since no one on TensorFlow is actively working on Jetson TX2 support (@benbarsdell works for NVidia).

Having a small code fragment to reproduce the issue would be helpful, but I understand its frustrating considering object detection is in the official tensorflow/models repo.
